<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 03:12:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>卢比将跟随亚洲货币走高，印度储备银行是 2024 年的关键因素</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-follow-asian-fx-higher-rbi-key-factor-2024-2023-12-29/</link><description>预计印度卢比周五开盘小幅走高，追随亚洲货币对美联储最早将于下季度转向的押注而上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 02:47:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-follow-asian-fx-higher-rbi-key-factor-2024-2023-12-29/</guid></item><item><title>随着智能手机激增，华为预计 2023 年收入增长 9%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-forecasts-9-revenue-growth-2023-smartphones-surge-2023-12-29/</link><description>路透社看到，轮值董事长胡厚昆在内部新年致辞中表示，中国科技巨头华为技术有限公司 (HWT.UL) 预计 2023 年收入将超过 7000 亿元人民币（985 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 02:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-forecasts-9-revenue-growth-2023-smartphones-surge-2023-12-29/</guid></item><item><title>前港独领导人在英国寻求庇护</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/former-hong-kong-independence-group-leader-seeks-asylum-britain-2023-12-28/</link><description>钟托尼 (Tony Chung) 于 2021 年根据中国实施的国家安全法被判入狱，他表示，他已逃往英国并正式申请政治庇护。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 22:11:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/former-hong-kong-independence-group-leader-seeks-asylum-britain-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>财新网原央行官员因受贿罪获刑16年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-central-bank-official-jailed-16-years-graft-caixin-2023-12-28/</link><description>随着执政的共产党加强对金融业的控制，一名前中国央行官员因受贿、泄露国家机密和内幕交易被判处 16 年零 6 个月的监禁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-central-bank-official-jailed-16-years-graft-caixin-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>会谈取得突破性进展后，中国军方猛烈抨击美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-military-lashes-out-us-after-breakthrough-talks-2023-12-28/</link><description>周四，在中美两国高级军事官员恢复高层会谈一周后，中国国防部猛烈抨击美国，批评美国继续干预亚太地区，并称其保持“冷战”思维。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:50:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-military-lashes-out-us-after-breakthrough-talks-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国计划到2025年建造全球一半以上的清洁燃料船舶</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/china-aims-build-over-half-worlds-clean-fuel-powered-ships-by-2025-2023-12-28/</link><description>工业部周四发布的指导方针中，中国设定了到2025年生产全球一半以上使用清洁燃料的船舶的目标。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/china-aims-build-over-half-worlds-clean-fuel-powered-ships-by-2025-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示不会对菲律宾一再“挑衅”视而不见</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-wont-turn-blind-eye-philippines-repeated-provocations-2023-12-28/</link><description>中国周四表示，在南海一系列冲突导致紧张局势加剧之际，中国不会对菲律宾一再的“挑衅和骚扰”视而不见。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:45:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-wont-turn-blind-eye-philippines-repeated-provocations-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促国民在骚乱中离开缅北地区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-nationals-leave-north-myanmar-region-amid-unrest-2023-12-28/</link><description>中国驻缅甸大使馆周四敦促中国公民尽快离开缅北果敢地区老街地区，理由是安全风险日益增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:28:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-nationals-leave-north-myanmar-region-amid-unrest-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>美军加强前沿部署 中国敦促地区保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-regional-alert-us-military-steps-up-forward-deployment-2023-12-28/</link><description>在有报道称美国计划恢复对日本发动原子弹轰炸的太平洋机场后，中国国防部周四敦促亚太地区保持高度戒备，因为美国加强了在该地区的军事部署。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-regional-alert-us-military-steps-up-forward-deployment-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责台湾“炒作”军事威胁并派遣战机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-taiwan-is-hyping-up-military-threat-its-own-gain-2023-12-28/</link><description>中国国防部周四指责台湾政府在两周多后的台湾选举前故意“炒作”中国的军事威胁，以获取选举利益，但却再次派战机进入台湾海峡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-taiwan-is-hyping-up-military-threat-its-own-gain-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>三名香港活动人士因“恐怖主义”炸弹阴谋被判最高六年监禁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/three-hong-kong-activists-jailed-up-6-years-terrorism-bomb-plot-2023-12-28/</link><description>三名香港活动人士周四被判处最高六年监禁，他们承认与 2021 年在广泛的民主抗议活动后计划在法院大楼和其他公共基础设施放置炸弹有关的指控。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/three-hong-kong-activists-jailed-up-6-years-terrorism-bomb-plot-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国小米推出首款电动汽车，计划成为顶级汽车制造商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-smartphone-maker-xiaomi-unveils-first-electric-vehicle-2023-12-28/</link><description>中国智能手机制造商小米周四揭开了其首款电动汽车的面纱，并立即宣布其目标是成为世界五大汽车制造商之一。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 06:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-smartphone-maker-xiaomi-unveils-first-electric-vehicle-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国12月份工厂活动可能连续第三个月萎缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-dec-factory-activity-likely-contracted-third-month-2023-12-28/</link><description>路透周四的一项民意调查显示，由于制成品需求疲软，中国制造业活动可能连续第三个月萎缩，这一数据将鼓励更多政策支持的呼声。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 05:15:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-dec-factory-activity-likely-contracted-third-month-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>越南“竹子外交”进入加速阶段</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-bamboo-diplomacy-shifts-into-higher-gear-2023-12-28/</link><description>共产党统治的越南升级了与世界头号强国的关系，包括前敌人中国和美国，作为其“竹子外交”的一部分，越南自 2021 年以来一直积极推行“竹子外交”，以应对日益加剧的全球紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:08:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-bamboo-diplomacy-shifts-into-higher-gear-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国在选举前向台湾有影响力的乐队施压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-pressures-influential-taiwanese-band-ahead-elections-sources-2023-12-28/</link><description>五月天被迫在选举前发表亲中国言论。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:04:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-pressures-influential-taiwanese-band-ahead-elections-sources-2023-12-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>